714788f-a.text:
The Battery Swedish Methodist Episcopal Church, 131-127 West 89th Street, north side, between Amsterdam and Columbus Avenues. This church will soon be remodeled into a motion picture theatre and by 1931 the theatre will be boarded up and offered for sale.
About 1925.
Brown Brothers.
